nodes.text: Star Wars Jedi Training Lightsaber Sound Book
Star Wars Jedi Training Lightsaber Sound Book is an announced young-readers title from Studio Fun International. It was scheduled for June 16, 2020, but was never officially released.
The online retailer Amazon.com originally listed a 2020 date for Star Wars Jedi Training Lightsaber Sound Book in 2018. As of March 16, 2021, it remains unpublished.
